Docker Components 
========================

Docker Daemon: its a server, long running program.

Rest-API: Its and interface for the communication between the docker demon and docker client.

Docker Client: A command lin interface which helps to interact with docker daemon via docker commands.

Docker Image
===============
Docker images are read-only templates with instructions to create a docker container. 
A Docker image is a file, comprised of multiple layers, that is used to execute code in a Docker container.


Docker Containers
===================
A Docker container image is a lightweight, standalone, executable package of software 
that includes everything needed to run an application: code, runtime, system tools, system libraries and settings.